Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.74,0:00:11.00,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Let’s go to the club room together, Rurino-chan!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:13.41,Rurino,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.89,0:00:15.46,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Let’s go, then, Kaho-chan.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:19.02,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where’s Sayaka-chan?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:21.99,Kaho,,0,0,0,,She went on ahead.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.30,0:00:24.99,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Come on, Rurino-chan! Hurry, hurry!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.07,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You’re just as energetic as ever, huh, Kaho-chan…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:32.68,Kaho,,0,0,0,,…Oh no.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.12,0:00:37.86,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Are you just about clocked out for today too…?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.81,0:00:45.05,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You’d think I was a new panda exhibit at the zoo with how much people wanted to talk to the new transfer…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:49.24,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I-I see…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.24,0:00:51.92,Kaho,,0,0,0,,But it’ll be okay!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:55.21,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We’ve got a special surprise for you!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.68,0:00:58.19,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Surprise…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:05.87,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Now, Rurino-chan!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:09.20,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Feast your eyes on the reborn School Idol Club!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.51,0:01:15.11,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I mean you say that, but it looks completely the same to me…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:19.11,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Um, good afternoon…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:27.85,Rurino,,0,0,0,,What.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:32.62,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Um, good afternoon…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:36.82,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Oh, good–\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:40.76,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Shhh, Tsuzuri-senpai! Not now!\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:44.36,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Am I getting hazed?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.84,0:01:48.32,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Heh heh heh…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.89,0:01:51.89,Kaho,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Rurino-chan?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:55.31,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Everyone in the club’s gonna ignore you as much as possible.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:02:00.20,Kaho,,0,0,0,,That way, even if you’re in the club room, it’ll be like you’re totally alone!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:03.00,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Total…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:04.75,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Total?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:06.12,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Total success?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:09.28,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Totally wrong…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:13.11,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Wrong…!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:15.11,Kaho,,0,0,0,,O-Oh…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:18.99,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I knew this was a bad idea…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.38,0:02:21.97,Kaho,,0,0,0,,It’s fine, it’s fine!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:24.07,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Okay, so for Plan B…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:27.19,Rurino,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:29.93,Rurino,,0,0,0,,What was this even supposed to be…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:36.93,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Hey, since today’s our last chance, I figured I’d throw things at the wall and see what sticks.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:41.99,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We wanted the School Idol Club to be a safe space for you!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:45.12,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We thought of plenty of ideas, so I hope you’re ready!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:48.99,Rurino,,0,0,0,,H-Huh…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:51.59,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Why are you going this far…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:56.80,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Well, even if we can’t come up with something good on our own,\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:03:01.51,Kaho,,0,0,0,,if we put our heads together, maybe we’ll figure something out!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:03.86,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,It was like that with us too, after all.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:06.28,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Right.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:08.02,Kozue,,0,0,0,,That’s how it happened.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:11.80,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We were thinking of ways for you to keep going,\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:18.10,Kaho,,0,0,0,,so stuff like how to keep your battery charged or how to continue even if your battery does die!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:23.67,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Hey, could you please tell us more about yourself, Rurino-chan?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.59,0:03:26.70,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:29.56,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Well, when I was in grade school…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:34.54,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I liked it when things were really fun.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:41.35,Rurino,,0,0,0,,When everyone around me was smiling, the fun times would just keep going.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:46.47,Rurino,,0,0,0,,But that’s actually really difficult.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:53.56,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Someone would get frustrated, and people would get upset.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:59.06,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And I would try to get everyone to get along…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:03.63,Rurino,,0,0,0,,At first, it was just so I could make sure we could keep having fun,\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:06.92,Rurino,,0,0,0,,but then I got completely used to doing it.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:10.67,Rurino,,0,0,0,,It would always weigh on me.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:16.16,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’d wonder if people in the group were getting bored or tired.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:22.21,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And I would always tell myself that if someone was starting to feel that way,\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:26.44,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’d do whatever I had to to make sure they would have fun again.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:34.25,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,If you kept thinking like that, then you would…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.89,0:04:36.55,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yeah…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:40.69,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’d wear myself out, right?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:45.45,Rurino,,0,0,0,,So I would spend more and more time by myself…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:47.45,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I understand…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:52.07,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Interpersonal relations are very difficult, aren’t they…?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:56.61,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And then, one day, I realized something.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:05:03.20,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Wow! Being alone is actually really fun!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:05.37,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:08.57,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That’s not where I thought this was going…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:15.89,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I don’t have to worry about other people, and I can do whatever I want!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:23.86,Rurino,,0,0,0,,The world’s my oyster! There’s nothing but fun to be had!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:28.38,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It’s a wonderful world!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:34.55,Rurino,,0,0,0,,After that, I stopped holding myself back.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:37.89,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I like having fun, so…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.55,0:05:42.76,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I would only chase after fun times! And then…!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:47.70,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Then, you joined the School Idol Club, right!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:51.30,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Uh, actually…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:56.94,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Thanks for letting us know more about you, Rurino-chan.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:03.08,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I didn’t know a thing about you until yesterday,\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:07.24,Kaho,,0,0,0,,so I’m really happy you’ve told us so much.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:10.43,Rurino,,0,0,0,,W-Well…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:16.55,Rurino,,0,0,0,,But, you’ve found out now, when it’s already too late…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:19.08,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:24.66,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, I said a lot of mean things that I shouldn’t have…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:28.90,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I don’t think of it like that.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:35.95,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You thought it might be fun, so you decided to try being a school idol, right?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:40.77,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Then, we should think of a way for you to continue being one!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:43.92,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…B-But…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:49.93,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You know, I was this close to quitting school!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:53.24,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Huh!? Why!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:59.20,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I thought that there was no way I could make my dreams come true here.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:02.00,Kaho,,0,0,0,,But it was alright!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:04.05,Kaho,,0,0,0,,It turned out okay!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:07.00,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Um…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:14.64,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,And I was very close to quitting this club myself.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:19.90,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Now, I’m working hard at both figure skating and being a school idol.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:26.98,Kaho,,0,0,0,,And until just recently, the second-years were fighting for like half a year!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:30.09,Kozue,,0,0,0,,It wasn’t a fight.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:35.27,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Your performance was so cool, Kozu.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:39.11,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Is that your new life motto?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:41.58,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…Why?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:43.58,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:49.27,Rurino,,0,0,0,,From what you’ve been telling me, everyone here has such strong personalities.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:57.89,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And yet, you all can go forward and be school idols together!? How!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:08:02.00,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ve had to try so hard this long…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:05.83,Rurino,,0,0,0,,How can you do it!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:08.52,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Because…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:11.88,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We’re school idols!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:15.74,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Because you’re school idols…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:17.88,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Yeah!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:21.30,Kaho,,0,0,0,,School idols are amazing.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.80,Kaho,,0,0,0,,No matter what they do, they do so freely!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:31.23,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You can do it for yourself, or for the people that support you,\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:35.25,Kaho,,0,0,0,,or to win Love Live!, or even just for fun!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:42.18,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Everyone’s different, so sometimes our ideas might clash, and maybe we’ll get into arguments…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:48.78,Kaho,,0,0,0,,But we’re all school idols, so we can acknowledge each other and move forward, hand in hand.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:55.34,Kaho,,0,0,0,,As long as you want to, it doesn’t matter what kind of personality you have.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:56.93,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You’ll still be a school idol!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:00.26,Kaho,,0,0,0,,So, Rurino-chan?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:02.73,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Don’t you want to try being a school idol?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:07.71,Kaho,,0,0,0,,If you want to, of course, we’ll give you our full support!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:12.78,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Because we’re all in this together, as girls who love school idols!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:14.78,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:16.78,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:20.10,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I want to try.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:27.16,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Even if you’re not the same, you can still face forward and have fun together.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:33.94,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I came here because the Hasunosora School Idol Club is what I aspire to be, so…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:39.57,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I want to try being a school idol!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:44.53,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ve been watching all this time, even when I was in California!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:46.84,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And I always thought that it looked so fun!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:54.74,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And as I watched the club, I realized that I wanted to be a part of it!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:59.13,Rurino,,0,0,0,,To be the same, yet completely different…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:04.39,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m the same, so I thought that as long as I’m together with all of you, maybe I might be able to do it.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:06.96,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Can I…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:11.00,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Can I be a school idol too…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:14.10,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Of course you can.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:17.00,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Even someone like me could come this far, after all.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:20.35,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I’m sure you can.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:22.40,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,We’re all here for you.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:29.61,Kozue,,0,0,0,,As long as you want to, you’ll be able to be a school idol.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:36.38,Rurino,,0,0,0,,But I can’t be around people without my battery running dry,\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:39.91,Rurino,,0,0,0,,and I’m the disrespectful water flea that ditched practice…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:43.66,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And most of all, I love being alone.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:48.89,Kaho,,0,0,0,,But you have fun when you’re together with everyone too, right?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:51.80,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I know that about you now, Rurino-chan!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:59.49,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…Am I not going to be a bother…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:02.44,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Of course not!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:05.37,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Running out of battery is just part of you, Rurino-chan!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:09.98,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Even if a flower bed has loads of different flowers, it doesn’t make it any less beautiful!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:16.04,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I want to be a school idol with you, Rurino-chan!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:20.81,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…Yeah! I do too!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:24.16,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Kaho-chan.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:25.89,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And everyone…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:29.81,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I’m fine, thank you!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:32.36,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Hehehe…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:35.49,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:38.06,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We never talked about that surprise we had!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:43.50,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:45.66,Rurino,,0,0,0,,There’s still something else?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:48.55,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Hehehe…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:54.65,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:56.68,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I call it the loner house!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:58.79,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…What.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:05.10,Kaho,,0,0,0,,So what do you think!? As long as you’re in there, you can be alone, no matter when!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:10.67,Kaho,,0,0,0,,And the inside’s dark and cramped, so I’m sure it’ll be relaxing! Nice idea, isn’t it!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:13.01,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Total…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:16.69,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Total? Totally awesome!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:23.61,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Totally wrong!!!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:25.20,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Wha–!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:38.66,Rurino,,0,0,0,,In any case, I’d like to become a full-fledged member, so…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:41.37,Rurino,,0,0,0,,W-What do you say to that!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:44.94,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Naturally, we accept.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:48.95,Kozue,,0,0,0,,It’s fine if your battery dies.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:53.48,Kozue,,0,0,0,,If anything, being able to communicate is more than enough.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.23,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Right, Tsuzuri?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:12:59.70,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I can do that now, right?\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:05.14,Kozue,,0,0,0,,That’s because Sayaka-san has worked very, very hard.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:10.73,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I’ve gotten pretty used to it recently, so you’re fine.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:14.72,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ahahaha, that’s pretty funny!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:17.90,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,She laughed. Nice job.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:22.53,Kaho,,0,0,0,,By the way, what do you want to do, Rurino-chan?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:26.72,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Our club does activities in subunits, right?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:34.94,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Are you asking whether she should learn under Kozue-senpai or Tsuzuri-senpai?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:38.12,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, nah!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:41.46,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ll go with Megu-chan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:45.32,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I came back to Japan for her, after all!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:49.89,Kaho,,0,0,0,,…Megu-chan?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:54.11,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Wait, who are you referring to?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:57.18,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Huh!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
